ActAn Act to amend the Fisheries Act and other Acts in consequence
SubjectOrder Fixing August 28, 2019 as the Date on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing August 28, 2019 as the date on which subsections 1(1), (5) and (10), sections 8, 13 and 19 to 24, subsections 25(2), (4), (5), (6), (8), (10) and (11) and 27(1) to (6), (8) and (9), sections 28 and 29, subsections 31(6) and (13), sections 52, and 55 to 57 and subsection 58(2) of AN ACT TO AMEND THE FISHERIES ACT AND OTHER ACTS IN CONSEQUENCE, chapter 14 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2019-0080 Publication Date: 2019-08-21
